item.description:
Weeelcome 2016!

This is my first post for the blog, and to up the ante I’ll post the super most secret which is my this year resolution!
okay, here’s the list in no particular order.

  • Get my hands on rotary engine and hands on learning
  • Improving my coding skills
  • Lose at least 10 kg and gain muscle
  • Gain Moar dosh money
  • Gain Moar powwr
  • Get good grades!
  • Make a journal
  • Start writing
  • Keep writing
  • Write more
  • Moar optimysticism


I really want to put pictures in this post and make it more interesting, but then I have not got that powerful on this writting thing yet, and I’m not sure I’m ready for such power. Just like what Om Benyamin says, “Lo makin kuat itu artinye tanggung jawab lo makin gede!”
